&lt;li&gt;Develop high-performance APIs, async workers, and application logic in Python and TypeScript.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ship user-facing product features and internal tools that make advanced AI systems useful and intuitive for customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and improve data ingestion, parsing, and analysis pipelines that transform raw customer interaction data into structured, actionable insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner across engineering, product, and design to translate ambiguous product ideas into robust technical systems.&lt;/li&gt;
